Construction Bank Says CBRC Approves Sales of Subordinated Bonds

-- B y   B i l l y   C h a n
-- 
2011-10-19T08:44:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/construction-bank-says-cbrc-approves-sales-of-subordinated-bonds.html
China Construction Bank Corp. (939)  said
the China Banking Regulatory Commission approved its plan to
sell as much as 40 billion yuan of subordinated bonds, according
to a statement to the Hong Kong stock exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Billy Chan in Hong Kong at 
